cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "AICP — Agent Interaction Content Protocol"
version: "0.1.0-dev"
abstract: >-
  AICP is an open content-layer protocol for agent-to-agent interaction.
  It provides enforceable, machine-checkable artifacts for policy-aware
  interoperability, attestations, and conformance.
authors:
  - family-names: "Volshebnik23"
keywords:
  - agent-to-agent
  - multi-agent
  - LLM agents
  - content-layer protocol
  - policy enforcement
  - orchestration
  - governance
  - attestations
  - interoperability standard
